OL,3,CIsrael approves death penalty for
OL,4,CPalestinians who murder Israelis
OL,6,FIsrael's parliament has passed a law
OL,7,Fapproving the death penalty for
OL,8,FPalestinians convicted of murdering
OL,9,FIsraelis.
OL,11,FThe bill's passage marked the
OL,12,Fculmination of a years-long push by
OL,13,FIsrael's far-right to escalate
OL,14,Fpunishment for Palestinians convicted
OL,15,Fof nationalistic offences against
OL,16,FIsraelis.
OL,18,FThe law makes the death penalty, by
OL,19,Fhanging, the default punishment for
OL,20,FWest Bank Palestinians convicted of
OL,21,Fnationalistic killings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774980702
OL,3,CIsrael approves death penalty for
OL,4,CPalestinians who murder Israelis
OL,6,FThe law also gives Israeli courts the
OL,7,Fauthority to impose either the death
OL,8,Fpenalty or life imprisonment on their
OL,9,Fown citizens. It is not retroactive
OL,10,Fand will apply only to future cases.
OL,12,FThe measure has been harshly condemned
OL,13,Fby Israeli and Palestinian rights
OL,14,Fgroups, who say it is racist,
OL,15,Fdraconian and unlikely to deter
OL,16,Fattacks by Palestinian attackers.
OL,18,FPrime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu came
OL,19,Fto the chamber to vote yes in person,
OL,20,Fand when the measure passed, the
OL,21,Fchamber erupted into cheers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774980702
OL,3,CIsrael approves death penalty for
OL,4,CPalestinians who murder Israelis
OL,6,FIsrael's firebrand minister of
OL,7,Fnational security, Itamar Ben-Gvir,
OL,8,Fwho spearheaded the push for the
OL,9,Flegislation, brandished a bottle in
OL,10,Fcelebration.
OL,12,FFar-right lawmaker Limor Son Har-
OL,13,FMelech, one of the bill's original
OL,14,Fsponsors, wiped tears from her eyes.
OL,15,FHar-Melech's first husband was killed
OL,16,Fby a Palestinian militant attack in
OL,17,Fthe West Bank.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774980702
OL,3,CIsrael approves death penalty for
OL,4,CPalestinians who murder Israelis
OL,6,FWithin minutes, the Association of
OL,7,FCivil Rights in Israel said it had
OL,8,Fpetitioned Israel's highest court,
OL,9,Fchallenging the law, calling it
OL,10,F"discriminatory by design" and
OL,11,F"enacted without legal authority" over
OL,12,FWest Bank Palestinians.
OL,14,FThe legislation calls for the death
OL,15,Fpenalty to go into effect within 30
OL,16,Fdays.
