CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774980702
OL,3,CIsrael approves death penalty for
OL,4,CPalestinians who murder Israelis
OL,6,FDirectly before voting began, Ben Gvir
OL,7,Fmade a bellowing speech from the
OL,8,Fpodium, describing the law as long
OL,9,Foverdue and a sign of strength and
OL,10,Fnational pride.
OL,12,F"From today, every terrorist will
OL,13,Fknow, and the whole world will know,
OL,14,Fthat whoever takes a life, the State
OL,15,Fof Israel will take their life," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FHe wore a lapel featuring a small
OL,19,Fmetal noose.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@`O]
