OL,3,CIsrael approves death penalty for
OL,4,CPalestinians who murder Israelis
OL,6,FCritics say that the bill establishes
OL,7,Fa hierarchy between Israeli court
OL,8,Fsystems in a way that will confine the
OL,9,Fdeath penalty to Palestinians
OL,10,Fconvicted of murdering Jewish citizens
OL,11,Fof Israel.
OL,13,FThe bill instructs military courts to
OL,14,Fmete out the sentence to those
OL,15,Fconvicted of murdering an Israeli "as
OL,16,Fan act of terror."
OL,26,@wD@cOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
