CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774980702
OL,3,CIsrael approves death penalty for
OL,4,CPalestinians who murder Israelis
OL,6,FSuch courts try only West Bank
OL,7,FPalestinians, who are not Israeli
OL,8,Fcitizens. The bill says military
OL,9,Fcourts can change the penalty to life
OL,10,Fimprisonment in "special
OL,11,Fcircumstances."
OL,13,FThe bill says executions should be
OL,14,Fcarried out within 90 days of
OL,15,Fsentencing.
