PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774980702
OL,3,CIsrael approves death penalty for
OL,4,CPalestinians who murder Israelis
OL,6,FThough Israel technically has the
OL,7,Fdeath penalty on the books as a
OL,8,Fpossible punishment for acts of
OL,9,Fgenocide, espionage during wartime and
OL,10,Fcertain terror offences, the country
OL,11,Fhasn't put anyone to death since Nazi
OL,12,Fwar criminal Adolf Eichmann in 1962.
OL,14,FThe bill will not apply retroactively
OL,15,Fto any of the militants Israel
OL,16,Fcurrently holds who attacked the
OL,17,Fcountry on October 7, 2023. There is a
OL,18,Fseparate bill under consideration
OL,19,Fdealing with punishment for the
OL,20,Fattackers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
