OL,3,CIsrael approves death penalty for
OL,4,CPalestinians who murder Israelis
OL,6,FSome opposition lawmakers worry that
OL,7,Fthe bill could harm future hostage
OL,8,Fnegotiations. Israel exchanged some
OL,9,F250 hostages taken during the October
OL,10,F2023 attack for thousands of
OL,11,FPalestinian prisoners.
